OL,3,C'Food has become almost inaccessible
OL,4,Cit's so expensive'
OL,6,FNew research says half of people
OL,7,Fgetting Universal Credit in Wales ran
OL,8,Fout of food within the last month.
OL,10,FThe Trussel Trust also found an
OL,11,Festimated 70,000 people claiming the
OL,12,Fbenefit had to use a food bank in the
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FThe charity's calling on the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment to develop a plan to end
OL,17,Fthe need for food banks.
OL,19,FThe Welsh Government said it's
OL,20,Fprovided #22m pounds since 2019 to
OL,21,Fsupport community food organisations.
