OL,3,C'Food has become almost inaccessible
OL,4,Cit's so expensive'
OL,6,FKathryn Wakeham is the chief executive
OL,7,Fof the Rumney forum - a poverty
OL,8,Felevation charity which helps support
OL,9,Fpeople with everyday essentials such
OL,10,Fas clothing, food, toys and homeware.
OL,12,FMs Wakeham has worked for the
OL,13,Forganisation over the last five years
OL,14,Fand says she's seen "enormous" change.
OL,16,F"This started as what I would say an
OL,17,Fempty shell with a few tables and a
OL,18,Fhandful of items and we've grown it to
OL,19,Fthis", she said.
