OL,6,F"We help hundreds of people throughout
OL,7,Fthe week. Sometimes right the way
OL,8,Fthrough the weekend we're still
OL,9,Fgetting calls and requests - one of us
OL,10,Fwill need to come up and help someone
OL,11,Fout in an emergency.
OL,13,F"The demand grew massively I would say
OL,14,Fover the last 18 months. It didn't
OL,15,Fbecome a gift anymore, it became a
OL,16,Fnecessity.
